in the semi-finals.

17:45.325 --> 17:48.110
I'm Beth, by the way.
Kenny Boland's mom.

17:53.594 --> 17:54.812
- We'll see you on the ice.

18:17.618 --> 18:20.273
Oh, it is hot in there.

18:21.883 --> 18:26.105
Wait a minute.
That sign is in dollars.

18:26.148 --> 18:28.324
