20:03.637 --> 20:05.465
- Can we please go?

20:05.508 --> 20:07.554
- I needed time to heal.
- All right.

20:07.597 --> 20:10.165
- They wanted to make sure I
could pass a solid, you know--

20:10.209 --> 20:12.428
- Let's get back in the bag.
- Come on, move it.

20:12.472 --> 20:14.038
