20:31.534 --> 20:33.754
- Call her from the road.

20:33.797 --> 20:37.192
- She's in a nursing home.
- Wait, what?

20:37.236 --> 20:40.630
Since when?
- She had a bad fall.

20:40.674 --> 20:43.111
- Well, what happened?
- I don't know.

20:43.154 --> 20:46.941
No one was taking care of her.
I was locked up.

20:46.984 --> 20:48.116
- No.

20:50.640 --> 20:54.688
- He should say goodbye to her.
- No.

20:54.731 --> 20:57.081
- She should say goodbye
