21:01.912 --> 21:04.567
- Manolo's good people.
He'll wait, right?

21:05.916 --> 21:10.530
He's solid.
He's a solid dude.

21:10.573 --> 21:13.576
- It is her last chance.

21:18.842 --> 21:22.237
One hour.

21:22.281 --> 21:23.891
Thank you.

21:23.934 --> 21:26.110
- All right, back in the bag.
Go on.

21:31.812 --> 21:33.944
- Deeply stupid.

21:38.253 --> 21:39.994
- You can't just
barge in here, okay?

21:40.037 --> 21:41.909
Why don't you ask that prick
