25:15.992 --> 25:17.907
What do we do?

25:20.170 --> 25:21.215
What do we do?
- I don't know.

25:21.258 --> 25:22.303
- Do we stay?
- I don't know.

25:22.346 --> 25:24.827
- Should we run?

25:32.705 --> 25:35.534
