26:06.086 --> 26:07.783
Where Nana at?

26:23.625 --> 26:27.890
- She lied, Annie.
- For months.

26:27.934 --> 26:31.459
- And she chose him over you.

26:31.502 --> 26:35.158
- And she's kind of racist.
- She's mostly racist.

26:35.202 --> 26:39.598
- She was here because
she fell on ice.

26:39.641 --> 26:43.863
- So?
- She was going to the salon.

26:43.906 --> 26:46.648
- It could have
happened anywhere.

26:46.692 --> 26:48.998
- I used to take her there.

26:56.615 --> 26:58.660
- All right.
- Okay.

26:58.704 --> 27:00.183
- Let's roll.

27:02.533 --> 27:04.318
Hold Nana, would you?

27:06.189 --> 27:07.234
She always liked you.

27:09.018 --> 27:11.717
Here.
- What's this?

27:11.760 --> 27:14.633
- Her final wish.

27:20.421 --> 27:22.292
- Lake Okoboji?

27:22.336 --> 27:26.166
- Yeah, that's where
she wants to be scattered.

27:26.209 --> 27:28.472
By the waterfall.
- That's beautiful.

27:28.516 --> 27:30.126
- That's three hours away.

27:30.170 --> 27:31.737
- It's where she married
Grandpa John.

27:31.780 --> 27:33.695
- We don't have time
for this, okay?

27:33.739 --> 27:35.697
- No, I gotta see it through.
- Look.

27:35.741 --> 27:37.612
She's a wonderful lady
and whatever,

27:37.656 --> 27:39.396
but we gotta get you to--

27:39.440 --> 27:40.702
- Canada.
- Yeah, right.

27:40.746 --> 27:42.965
- I'm not going.

27:43.009 --> 27:44.837
- Yeah, you are.
- No, I'm not.

27:44.880 --> 27:46.273
- We don't answer to you.

27:46.316 --> 27:48.405
- Yeah, we answer to someone
way scarier than you.

27:48.449 --> 27:50.843
- Why does that guy
give a turd where I go, huh?

28:02.115 --> 28:03.725
You know what?

28:03.769 --> 28:05.771
Thanks for the ride.
You're off the hook.

28:05.814 --> 28:07.120
- Uh-uh.
No way.

28:07.163 --> 28:10.210
- Annie, I dig your new hair.
- Not really new.

28:10.253 --> 28:13.604
- Well, I like that you
let the roots grow out.

28:13.648 --> 28:16.695
Hey, hey.
- Beth.

28:16.738 --> 28:18.087
- Hey.
Turn off the child locks.

28:18.131 --> 28:21.177
- Beth, what are you doing?
- Give me Nana back!

28:22.918 --> 28:24.267
- Get back in the bag.

28:26.748 --> 28:30.404
- No, don't.
- Get back in the bag, Boomer.

28:32.145 --> 28:34.582
- If we didn't have
enough reasons to go to hell.

28:34.625 --> 28:38.455
- I swear to God this will be
her final resting place.

28:38.499 --> 28:40.066
- Beth, don't!

28:40.109 --> 28:43.678
- Oh, she's gonna go so well
with all this old people stuff.

28:43.722 --> 28:44.940
